data.description: Great home located in the neighborhood of  Tranquil Acres.This home boasts several appealing features.The living areas of the house are adorned with beautiful hardwood floors,  adding a touch of elegance and warmth to the interior.The home includes an elegant dining room, perfect for hosting and entertaining guests. It's a great space for special meals and gatherings.The living area features sliding wood barn doors that lead to an additional space. This space could serve as an office or playroom, providing flexibility to adapt to your family's needs. The kitchen is well-lit and equipped with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Natural light in the kitchen is always a plus for those who enjoy cooking or spending time there. With threespacious bedrooms, there's plenty of room for family members and guests to enjoy comfortable and private spaces. Outdoor Living: The 16' x 27' deck provides an excellent outdoor space for relaxation and entertaining. It's also shaded by two large live oak trees, offering a serene environment for outdoor activities. The property seems to offer a balance between indoor and outdoor living in a tranquil neighborhood setting. If you're interested in this home, it's advisable to act quickly to seize this excellent opportunity in Ladson.
